title: fanoutqa: Can you provide the orbit speed (km/s) about the planets in our solar system? (83c8ef40f22c9f72)

chat_history.content: Can you provide the orbit speed (km/s) about the planets in our solar system?

I found the following orbit speeds of the planets in our solar system:
- Mercury: 47.87 km/s
- Venus: 35.02 km/s
- Earth: 29.78 km/s
- Mars: 24.077 km/s
- Jupiter: 13.07 km/s
- Saturn: 9.69 km/s
- Uranus: 6.80 km/s
- Neptune: 5.43 km/s

Would you like to know more about any of these planets?
